===Verb===
'''werden'''

#plural past tense of [[worden]]

----
==German==
===Verb===
'''werden''' (''third-person singular simple present'' '''[[wird]]''', ''[[past tense]]'' '''[[wurde]]''', ''[[past participle]]'' '''[[geworden]]''' (or [[worden]], see below), auxiliary verb '''[[sein]]''')

# [[will]]
#:''Ich '''werde''' nach Hause gehen'' - I will go home
# auxiliary verb for the passive (participle: ''[[worden]]'')
#:''Das Buch wird gerade gelesen'' - The book is being read
#:''Er war geschlagen worden'' - He had been beaten
# [[become]], [[get]]
#:''Es '''wird''' heißer'' - It's getting hotter

